  "body": "This is a feature request to have a way to enable Ethereum Improvement Proposals (EIPs) that are supported by [Ethereum-js](https://ethereumjs.github.io/) for the Hardhat Network.\r\n\r\nThe use case I have at the moment is to test the gas changes in [EIP-2929](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-2929) in the upcoming Berlin fork.\r\n\r\nAs per [EthereumJs](https://github.com/ethereumjs/ethereumjs-vm/blob/c9c76bb31f8fa7f5b746e8dca729e0fb8d6a0744/packages/common/README.md#eips) doco, the following EIPs are currently supported:\r\n* EIP-2537: BLS precompiles\r\n* EIP-2929: gas cost increases for state access opcodes\r\n",
