    "body": "If I understand correctly EIP-2537 has been pushed back and is now not included in any of the hardforks in ethereum-js. Is there an easier way to enable them other than overriding the node config in the provider at https://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/blob/98b7548525080c91a45cc3d3971f2d0248f62695/packages/hardhat-core/src/internal/hardhat-network/provider/provider.ts#L216 ?\r\n\r\nEdit: on second thought, that wouldn't work because a new config field wouldn't get picked up. So one would have to override `HardhatNode.create` https://github.com/nomiclabs/hardhat/blob/98b7548525080c91a45cc3d3971f2d0248f62695/packages/hardhat-core/src/internal/hardhat-network/provider/node.ts#L154",
