    "updated_at": "2021-09-08T02:52:09Z",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Thanks for the replies. If anyone else wants to try something in this direction modifying the return value of `Common.forCustomChain` from `ethereumjs` with the following in `hardhat.config.js` seems to do the trick.\r\n\r\n```js\r\nrequire(\"@nomiclabs/hardhat-waffle\");\r\n\r\nconst Common = require(\"@ethereumjs/common\").default;\r\nconst forCustomChain = Common.forCustomChain;\r\nCommon.forCustomChain = (...args) => {\r\n  const common = forCustomChain(...args);\r\n  common._eips = [2537];\r\n  return common;\r\n};\r\n```",
